::Primal Prime::

    He soon arrived at the scene. He saw the three dinobots and it brought 
back flashes of bots. He saw Grimlock and a few other dinobots, he could only 
place the name on Grimlock. He then awoke from the dream. 
    He looked down at the Cheetah, the cat reminded Primal of someone. He 
just couldn't place the name.
    "I am Primal, I'm a new Maximal here, I take it you are also?" He asked 
Cheetor. Then he went over to the Dinobots. "Are you from the new ship that 
has arrived?"




    "He doesn't look trustworthy." (omit that, I'm messing with Earth2025)
